Welcome to the W3C {{ group.name }}

The group meets in weekly teleconferences (currently Tuesday at 1500 UTC/11 Eastern).
Agendas are shared the day before. Connection information is available to group participants.

We use the mailing list public-web-adv@w3.org and the github repository 
https://github.com/w3c/web-advertising/
See https://github.com/w3c/web-advertising/blob/master/BG-how-we-work.md 


The following link will lead you to a "facility map" 
with additional information about the group and W3C resources.

https://w3c.github.io/Guide/participant/group.html?gid={{ group.id }}


